          <h3 class="ba-title">Yext Reviews — Best directory + review combo</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For businesses that already need Yext for directory management and want review monitoring bundled in.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Yext is primarily a directory management platform — syncing business data to 200+ directories. But its review monitoring features make it a reasonable combo tool for businesses already paying for directory sync. Aggregates reviews from multiple platforms, allows response from a unified dashboard, and manages role-based access for multi-location teams. The review generation features are basic — for serious volume generation, Yext needs a Podium or NiceJob alongside it.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Directory sync + review monitoring in one subscription</h4><p>If you need directory management anyway, getting review monitoring bundled eliminates a second subscription.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Unified response dashboard with multi-location role-based access</h4><p>Respond to reviews from the same dashboard where you manage directory listings. Clean for multi-location organizations.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>200+ directory coverage paired with review aggregation</h4><p>The broadest combination of directory accuracy and review visibility in one tool.</p></div></li>
