        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#8 · $39-59/MO · BEST BUDGET MONITORING</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">BrightLocal — Best budget review monitoring</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For local businesses that want review monitoring bundled with rank tracking and citation auditing at the lowest price point.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">BrightLocal is a local SEO platform with solid review monitoring built in. It aggregates from Google, Yelp, Facebook, and TripAdvisor with real-time alerts. Review showcase widgets can be embedded on your website. The geo-grid rank tracker and citation audit are the main reasons most businesses choose BrightLocal — the review monitoring is a useful bonus. The limitation: no review generation tools, no response capabilities from the dashboard, no sentiment analysis.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Review monitoring from major platforms with real-time alerts</h4><p>Google, Yelp, Facebook, TripAdvisor in one dashboard. Email alerts when new reviews come in. Review showcase widgets for your website.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Bundled with geo-grid rank tracking and citation auditing</h4><p>The best combination of review monitoring + local ranking data at this price point. One subscription covers both needs.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>$39-59/month — the most affordable option with real multi-platform coverage</h4><p>No other tool in this list covers monitoring across multiple major platforms at under $60/month.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: monitoring only — no generation, no response tools</h4><p>BrightLocal tells you about reviews but doesn't help you get more of them or respond from its dashboard. For review generation, add NiceJob at $75/mo.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- #9 Trustpilot -->
    <div class="ba-grid" id="tool-9" style="margin-top: 48px;">
