          <p class="ba-sub">For ecommerce brands and B2B companies that want verified buyer reviews with Google star ratings in search results.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Trustpilot is a review platform, not a multi-platform monitoring tool. Businesses collect reviews on Trustpilot itself, which integrates with Google to show star ratings in organic search results — the "rich snippet" effect that increases CTR significantly for ecommerce and B2B. The free tier provides basic profile and response functionality. The trade-off for local businesses: Trustpilot only manages Trustpilot reviews. Your Google, Yelp, and Facebook reviews live elsewhere.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Google rich snippet integration adds star ratings to search results</h4><p>Verified Trustpilot ratings can appear directly in Google search results. For ecommerce, this increases CTR and drives qualified traffic.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Verified review collection from confirmed buyers</h4><p>Trustpilot verifies that reviewers are actual customers, increasing the credibility of the rating. Integrates with Shopify, WooCommerce, and major ecommerce platforms.</p></div></li>
