          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: manages Trustpilot reviews only — not multi-platform</h4><p>For local businesses, Google, Yelp, and Facebook reviews matter more than Trustpilot. Don't prioritize Trustpilot at the expense of building local platform presence.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

