        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Completely free — direct response capability to all reviews</h4><p>Respond to every Google review from the GBP dashboard or mobile app. The most important review platform for local SEO, accessible at no cost.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Direct local search ranking impact</h4><p>Review count, average rating, and response rate all directly influence local pack rankings. No other review platform has as direct a ranking effect for local businesses.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Q&amp;A management and basic review analytics included</h4><p>See impressions, queries, and actions. Manage Q&A to pre-answer common questions. Mobile app handles on-the-go review responses.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: Google reviews only, no automation, no multi-platform monitoring</h4><p>GBP is the baseline, not the complete solution. Add BrightLocal for monitoring, NiceJob for generation, or theStacc for GBP post automation — depending on your gap.</p></div></li>
